@ontos 1.0
@title Team knowledge example
@type team-knowledge
@updated 2026-06-05

- Maintainer knowledge @id(maintainer-knowledge) #team #knowledge
  status: active
  owner: maintainers
  purpose: Keep recurring project decisions easy to find.
  current:
    - Naming decisions are documented in docs/NAMING.md.
    - Release decisions are documented in docs/RELEASE_PROCESS.md.
  ai_task: Answer contributor questions using only public repository context.
  ai_boundary: Avoid inventing commitments not recorded in docs.
  risk:
    - Knowledge may become stale if decisions are not linked.
  verify:
    - Check references after moving documentation.
    - Run public surface scan after editing public text.
  history:
    - 2026-06-05 created official team knowledge example.

  - Naming decisions @id(naming-decisions) #naming
    status: stable
    depends_on: [[maintainer-knowledge]]
    acceptance:
      - Repository name remains ontos-protocol.
      - CLI command remains ontosfmt.

    - Contributor answer @id(contributor-answer) #support
      purpose: Explain naming without mentioning unrelated projects.
      verify:
        - Answer links to docs/NAMING.md.
